title: Ultra Detailed Displacement Maps for Victoria 7
description:
Link: http://www.daz3d.com/ultra-detailed-displacement-maps-for-victoria-7

Details

Bring additional realism to your renders by means of high-quality displacement maps for the following parts of the body: head, torso and limbs. The product is equally effective for work with 3Delight and Iray Renders. Options of loading, incrceasing and decreasing relief strength and the possibility of removal is provided. The product supports 1 UV set for Genesis 3 Female(s): Victoria 7
